{"tid":1807952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新口號：香港人奪權！","createTime":"2020-01-02T05:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T10:02:22.000Z","uid":221927,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"453f7e9b02a61c01e657ef106b3b2e06d8e20885","tid":1807952,"uid":221927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"口號好影響抗爭方針同意向<br />\n加油報仇呢d無實質方向而且會比人質疑，不如用｢奪權｣一字取代。<br />\n<br />\n香港如今落得如斯田地，乃因香港人沒有實權，權力掌控在部份奶共港人手上，要解困局，我們必須要取得權力，無論係港人治港/五大訴求/自治/獨立，我們必須要掌權才能實現，此口號可以強化香港人決心，令不會止步於日後五大訴求偽實行，直到取得實權。<br />\n<br />\n所以，跟我讀一次：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人奪權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外國際線可以改為Fight for freedom,  Boycott China.  <br />\n香港人奪權英文版歡迎大家提出集思廣益。"},{"pid":"090da264d3025ca7f50386957b3a31fc3c31ab53","tid":1807952,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"58db6761eee8560493209158dbcd88ea3c7af0fb","tid":1807952,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"靜靜地啦 講埋出口咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dae05242a7ff7ddc9d65b5495e85d3a7f5ea58","tid":1807952,"uid":309148,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:34:53.000Z","msg":"奪乜L嘢權<br />\n主權一向都只係屬於香港人<br />\n港共中公先係剽取權力嗰個"},{"pid":"0806bbf6f6596c2162920b28ffe7f2f8ec922ae0","tid":1807952,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:35:35.000Z","msg":"中文差唔怪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c17102075ce2063e522b634556984e0fcc4422","tid":1807952,"uid":221927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58db6761eee8560493209158dbcd88ea3c7af0fb","tid":1807952,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"靜靜地啦 講埋出口咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"